snippet.title: Will Schoder
snippet.description:
I make videos on things I care about. Re-enchantment, metamodernism, and meaning mostly. 

(Conformity [Alienation] -/- Congruence [Wisdom] -/- Chaos [Anomie])
                                                                   ^

"I have striven not to laugh at human actions, not to weep at them, nor to hate them, but to understand them." -Baruch Spinoza
